{"tid":2286243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭家麒: 有成員曾期望美方外交交涉　勿輕易制裁香港","createTime":"2020-11-14T22:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T02:59:01.000Z","uid":126889,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e8579b3557c37e7b3dcda123c5128608ea132f8d","tid":2286243,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T22:09:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559980-20201114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559980-20201114.htm&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BC1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=be35a5ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559980-20201114.htm&h=1d3d51f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559980-20201114.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n被取消立法會議員資格的郭家麒表示，有成員曾經向美方表示不要輕易制裁香港。<br />\n<br />\n他出席一個電台節目時回應有說法指公民黨要求美國制裁香港，<span class=\"red\">他表示有成員曾經在美國</span>，向美方表示不要輕易制裁香港，因為香港不想受經濟打擊，只是當時沒有向外透露，又說公民黨都希望香港亂局會停，希望對方以外交途徑與中方或香港交涉。<br />\n<br />\n出席同一節目的民主派會議召集人胡志偉表示，如果因為犯錯誤招致別人制裁，再找代罪羔羊，只是反映政權的橫蠻無理。至於有說法認為由於民主派拉布，令4名議員被取消資格，他重申個多月來，民主派一直根據議事規則點算人數，是合規矩。"},{"pid":"6b8447a70a57d3ef9975fe5432d80f330808c05c","tid":2286243,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T22:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又要威又要戴頭盔"},{"pid":"4e2af0953a4eef9aebe3989852a338b6ee386cd0","tid":2286243,"uid":60527,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T22:25:45.000Z","msg":"飛機師？<br />\n果陣好似比劉細良屌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e26cf345045505ffd03dfd73671e7eb33d3d63","tid":2286243,"uid":154486,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T22:27:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>你班人仲同美國國務院報串埋袁弓夷添我屌你老母</strong></span>"},{"pid":"30426de101742c25d1dfeac1f09ddf8f71d836aa","tid":2286243,"